
::–– Build XGraphics.dll ––::
windres XGraphics.rc -O coff -o XGraphics.res
g++ -s -std=c++17 -shared -m64 -O2 -static-libgcc -static-libstdc++ -o XGraphics.dll XGraphics.cpp XGraphics.res -lgdiplus -lgdi32 -luser32

